Stage 3

Sprint Workflow

We split your project details into actionable development tasks. Your developer will then initiate a weekly 'Sprint' cycle that includes several tasks, all aimed to be completed by the week's end. As each task is completed, it will be flagged for review throughout the week."

Tasks

Stage 4

Submit Unlimited Tasks & Revisions

We’ll refine each task until you’re fully satisfied. Once a task is approved, we proceed to the next one, and a fresh sprint is initiated each week with new tasks. If a task from the previous sprint is still ongoing, it will carry over into the new sprint.
